1.6
log
@shm_open(), sysconf(), tcflow(), and tcsendbreak() are not permitted to be
cancellation points in POSIX, so change them to invoke the non-cancellation
point versions of open(), close(), nanosleep(), and write()

ok deraadt@@ millert@@
